## We can make something that slows down the velocity of the wheel so it hits zero at some point that we decide beforehand. When spin wheel is clicked, a random number generator decides which place will be chosen, and that spot on the wheel will get a certain value, from 0-24. Each slice has an equal chance to be selected, and the wheel will spin and land on that slice chosen. It will then set the money per letter to that value, and will change when spun again.
